      "name": "Mesh independence verification — shear stress distribution",
      "description": "Three mesh densities (coarse 4.1M, medium 8.7M, fine 12.4M elements) were compared for scalar shear stress distributions at the impeller trailing edge. GCI index between medium and fine meshes was 1.8%, below the 5% threshold.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/morrison/activity/mesh-independence-study-2023-09"
    },
    {
